Package com.zoubworld.java.math

Class BigRational

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Number
com.zoubworld.java.math.BigRational
All Implemented Interfaces:
IBasicOperator, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<BigRational>
public class BigRational
extends java.lang.Number
implements java.lang.Comparable<BigRational>, IBasicOperator
Compilation: javac Rational.java Execution: java Rational Immutable ADT for Rational numbers. Invariants ----------- - gcd(num, den) = 1, i.e, the rational number is in reduced form - den >= 1, the denominator is always a positive integer - 0/1 is the unique representation of 0 We employ some tricks to stave of overflow, but if you need arbitrary precision rationals, use BigRational.java. 1st autor : Copyright © 2000–2017, Robert Sedgewick and Kevin Wayne. Last updated: Fri Oct updated: 2019, Pierre Valleau
